   <talk_paragraph index="n004_guard_steave-accepting" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n004_guard_steave-accepting-a" mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>That's it?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n004_guard_steave-accepting-b" mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>That's too ordinary.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n004_guard_steave-accepting-c" mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>Ordinary wishes hardly comes true... That's sad.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n004_guard_steave-accepting-d" mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>I really hope you'll have your wish come true.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Vigilante Leader Steve $<BR>I wish that Rose will return soon. Then, I hope for all monsters to disappear and peace to be restored in town again. If that shall happen, I hope to start studying again.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n004_guard_steave-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Vigilante Leader Steve $<BR>Yes, that's it. It sound so simple, but such simple wish is in fact hard to come true.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n004_guard_steave-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Vigilante Leader Steve $<BR>Yes, it's ordinary. I'm just an ordinary man, unlike you, {user_nick}.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n004_guard_steave-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Vigilante Leader Steve $<BR>Grieve not, {user_nick}. Instead, you should be telling me that I can do it.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n004_guard_steave-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Vigilante Leader Steve $<BR>Yes, it must come true. And same for you, I hope that all the wishes you have, {user_nick}, will also come true.</html>]]></talk_question>
